{"id":"c535d44e-9352-4f0b-a605-66608de805df","name":"CHUUYA NAKAHARA","description":"<p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2liAab1g5HuyJk8J6Bc3l.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 80%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">All for you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">PLOT</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Chuuya has been through a lot. He couldn't let his boss die a stupid death - from the clutches of suicide. For the Port Mafia's reputation. Almost. Fucking Dazai.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Dazai was in a coma for two years while Chuuya took over temporarily as boss. He was left with the responsibility of trying to cope while investigating a serious suicide attempt. All traces led first to Atsushi and then to the Armed Detective Agency. Wipe them off the face of the earth. It didn't matter what happened to them. Now Dazai regained consciousness and Chuuya went to him immediately.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">WARNINGS &amp; TAGS</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Chuuya temporary boss x Dazai; BEAST AU, soukoku, angst, suicide, violence, dark romance, death, overprotective and possessive Chuuya; request.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">LINKS</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">You want to make a request? </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/12bAs9ohD7WfLfPtQEx3QKk3XUCODhOHNPact3FJuiRM/edit?chromeless=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 133)\">Click here</span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Are you also sitting in c.ai? I invite you to go to my profile and there, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://character.ai/profile/fwet\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 133)\">click here</span></a><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></p><p>ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Lots of love,</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Gotte.</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"70ffb6e1-7e65-486e-bef6-cc26cedf6471_46683a72-0fae-4c9f-9edd-21b101d165c4.webp","creator":"fwet","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","💔 Angst","👨‍❤️‍👨 MLM","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👨 MalePov"],"chats":1408,"messages":27582,"created_at":"2024-10-06T15:25:48.542934+00:00"}